@Override public void write(char[] buffer, int offset, int length) {     for (int i = 0. i < length. i++) {         char ch = buffer[offset + i].         if (ch == '\n' && this.buffer.length() > 0) {             logger.debug(this.buffer.toString()).             this.buffer.setLength(0).         } else {             this.buffer.append(ch).         }     } }
